OL,3,CProtest over eviction of NHS staff
OL,4,Cfrom hospital flats
OL,6,FA protest has been held after dozens
OL,7,Fof NHS staff were told they face
OL,8,Feviction from hospital accommodation.
OL,10,FAlmost 80 workers at Rotherham
OL,11,FHospital have received letters saying
OL,12,Fthat the on-site flats, where some of
OL,13,Fthem have lived for several years, are
OL,14,Fnot fit for purpose.
OL,16,FThe 1970s accommodation blocks provide
OL,17,Faffordable homes, including for many
OL,18,Finternational workers.
