OL,4,Cfrom hospital flats
OL,6,FBut the trust which runs the hospital
OL,7,Fsaid it has to close three of the
OL,8,Fbuildings after they were identified
OL,9,Fas a fire risk.
OL,11,FProtesters gathered outside the
OL,12,Fhospital on Monday calling for the
OL,13,Fdecision to be reversed and for
OL,14,Frepairs to be carried out.
OL,16,FOne worker, who has lived on the site
OL,17,Ffor 12 years and did not want to be
OL,18,Fidentified, said: "It just came
OL,19,Ftotally out of the blue.
