OL,3,CProtest over eviction of NHS staff
OL,4,Cfrom hospital flats
OL,6,F"There's a very limited (rental)
OL,7,Fmarket available in Rotherham.
OL,8,FCertainly the prices I've seen aren't
OL,9,Fcomparable for myself or anybody on my
OL,10,Fkind of income at the moment.
OL,12,F"It's a really big worry because it's
OL,13,Fpotentially a situation where you're
OL,14,Fgoing to be made homeless. There's no
OL,15,Fattempt to communicate with us or
OL,16,Fassess the likely impact. (I feel)
OL,17,Fabsolutely betrayed."
