OL,3,CProtest over eviction of NHS staff
OL,4,Cfrom hospital flats
OL,6,FThe Rotherham NHS Foundation Trust
OL,7,Fsaid it "understood the concerns"
OL,8,Fbeing raised and had held "listening
OL,9,Fevents" to try to address those
OL,10,Fworries.
OL,12,FBut Rotherham MP Sarah Champion said
OL,13,Fthe way the situation had been handled
OL,14,Fwas "appalling".
OL,16,F"Having a note shoved under your door
OL,17,Ftelling you you are going to be made
OL,18,Fhomeless is not the way we treat our
OL,19,FNHS staff," she said.
