OL,3,CProtest over eviction of NHS staff
OL,4,Cfrom hospital flats
OL,6,F"Secondly, I know that they are trying
OL,7,Freally hard to rectify this but we
OL,8,Fneed to understand the trauma this has
OL,9,Fcaused people but also that some
OL,10,Fpeople came here from around the world
OL,11,Fto help Rotherham, to help the NHS.
OL,13,F"The accommodation, they thought, was
OL,14,Fpart of their package, so to have that
OL,15,Ftaken away was really devastating."
OL,17,FA trust spokesperson said no tenants
OL,18,Fhad been asked to leave before the end
OL,19,Fof their leases.
