OL,4,Cfrom hospital flats
OL,6,FThey added: "One to one meetings have
OL,7,Fbeen offered to all 76 residents so
OL,8,Ftheir needs can be understood and
OL,9,Fsolutions developed to resolve the
OL,10,Fsituation.
OL,12,F"The trust is committed to working
OL,13,Fwith those residents affected by these
OL,14,Fchanges to assist them in finding
OL,15,Falternative accommodation and to
OL,16,Fretain them at the Trust for the
OL,17,Fbenefit of patients."
